---
const PORTRAIT = 'https://ozxbjwvwchesjgebenbv.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/media/1180cabe-49ef-4812-9883-310f8153852b.webp';
---
<section class="maker">
  <div class="maker__grid">
    <div class="maker__portrait">
      <img src={PORTRAIT} alt="German Silver Navajo Pearls" />
    </div>
    <div class="maker__body">
      <div class="maker__eyebrow">◆ German Silver Navajo Pearls</div>
      <h2 class="maker__title">German silver, <em>Navajo made.</em></h2>
      <p class="maker__body-copy">
        Although not sterling silver, each bead is an alloy mixture of German silver
        and white bronze. Harder than sterling, German silver looks much the same but
        boasts wonderful durability and tarnish resistance. From the mid 1800s, Native
        American tribes began crafting adornments from this beautiful metal alloy.
        Native-made German silver jewelry is a true artform.
      </p>
      <p class="maker__body-copy">
        Our Navajo artists beautifully antique and hand polish each German silver
        bead, giving it the same lifelong quality with all of the look and weight of a
        solid sterling Navajo pearl — and at a fantastic price.
      </p>
      <div class="maker__sign">
        <span class="verse">Hand antiqued · Hand polished</span>
        <span class="dash">—</span>
        <span class="name">Navajo artists</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
